Target: An ontology developed for representing the United Stations (UN) Sustainable Development Goals (SDGs).

Comment: An objective specification which describes the endpoint of a development process following the Sustainable Development Agenda for 2030 [SDGIO Ontology, Accessed on 29 October 2020]

A threshold value of a sustainable development indicator value or a set of threshold values of several such indicators towards or beyond which corresponding indicator values from a socio-economic-environmental system should tend in order to meet a sustainable development goal [SDGIO ontology, Accessed 29 October 2020]
A data item which represents a sustainable development goal indicator in some quantitative or qualitative system of measurement [SDGIO ontology, Accessed on 29 October 2020]
